for nearly 20 years,

02:25.078 --> 02:26.880
but these days, I'm away a lot.

02:26.913 --> 02:28.982
I'm back here for a charity
event in a few days,

02:29.015 --> 02:31.584
and before I hit the road again,
I'm gonna go out

02:31.618 --> 02:32.919
and see the people and places

02:32.952 --> 02:34.921
I've been missing
since I've been gone.

02:34.954 --> 02:38.057
♪ Come and dance with me ♪
<b></b>
♪ I gotta, I gotta ♪

02:38.091 --> 02:39.926
♪ Come dance with me,
come dance with me ♪

