at that point.

10:08.908 --> 10:12.612
It's hard to imagine
the less than zero,

10:12.645 --> 10:14.880
bright lights, big city time
being beaten.

10:14.914 --> 10:16.215
I agree.
I'm with you.

10:16.248 --> 10:17.883
It might -- I was drivin'
my kid to school.

10:17.917 --> 10:20.186
