"Yeah, you know,

10:20.219 --> 10:21.420
One Direction
is kind of like

10:21.454 --> 10:23.222
the Led Zeppelin
of our generation."

10:23.255 --> 10:25.257
-No, please don't say that.
-And I slammed on the brakes,

10:25.291 --> 10:27.560
