doin' blow on the pizza lag.
-Yeah.

10:36.469 --> 10:38.971
Those were the days.
Those were the days.

10:39.005 --> 10:40.773
Let me get
one more bite.

10:40.806 --> 10:43.409
Try a bite of that Sicilian.
It's cooled down enough.

10:43.442 --> 10:45.778
♪♪

10:45.811 --> 10:48.147
-Mm. That's delicious.
-Yeah. Thanks, guys.

10:48.180 --> 10:49.982
-Thank you. Take care.
-Thanks for comin'.

10:50.016 --> 10:51.751
-That was awesome.
-Let's hang more.

10:51.784 --> 10:53.786
-Dude, let's have a weekend.
-Let's have a silly dinner.

10:53.819 --> 10:56.122
Let's have one of our old
weekends together.
<b></b>
Yes, yes, exactly.

10:56.155 --> 10:58.557
Reedus: I love the stories
that live in these walls.

10:58.591 --> 10:59.925
No matter how long I'm here,

10:59.959 --> 11:03.195
